{"tid":1851573,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"葉劉淑儀: 反對全面封關，只限制內地人入境，是不合比例和帶有歧視性。","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T08:54:00.000Z","uid":167469,"like":13,"dislike":242,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2a1bd6b303075a3fbb2e492dcdc4354da3a8b4","tid":1851573,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:46:31.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情陰霾籠罩全城，有前線醫護人員工會早前要求港府全面封關，否則不排除發起罷工。行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表明反對相關建議。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">她認為，若所有外國人、內地人和香港人不能入境，香港會變成孤城，如果只限制內地人入境，亦是不合比例和有歧視性，強調假設所有內地人都帶病無科學根據，但她認為政府可收集數據，限制內地有廣泛爆發地區的人來港。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n對於目前市面口罩短缺，葉劉淑儀稱，懲教署正加緊生產口罩，而署方有聯繫東莞廠家有口罩生產機器和物料，當局可以利用空置工業大廈加強本地生產。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2364368/反對全面封關+葉劉:假設內地人帶病無科學根據?fbclid=IwAR2L8Te_AjwvX_EsvCca_Ai4QuHWKtGWk7U6o6foudHpo2Hkb8rNGYnHS64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2364368%2F%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C%2B%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%3A%E5%81%87%E8%A8%AD%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%B6%E7%97%85%E7%84%A1%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2L8Te_AjwvX_EsvCca_Ai4QuHWKtGWk7U6o6foudHpo2Hkb8rNGYnHS64&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=46f071ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2364368/反對全面封關+葉劉:假設內地人帶病無科學根據?fbclid=IwAR2L8Te_AjwvX_EsvCca_Ai4QuHWKtGWk7U6o6foudHpo2Hkb8rNGYnHS64</a>"},{"pid":"a6ad65f33088423d12e0c46bb0fcab6828b4d67a","tid":1851573,"uid":242537,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"你咁撚大愛....<br />\n死返去同武漢人做愛啦"},{"pid":"4402c19cfdafdfbd707ffab7731219d54d31f4b2","tid":1851573,"uid":223643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"【疫情展望】手足做好防護措施，去到 Phase II. 就仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n不理香港人健康，是帶歧視性的"},{"pid":"ed4c5501fd19c5997dd619f9b2eaba73694c903e","tid":1851573,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"政府一日唔全面封關，只會鼓勵更多疫區感染者衝入香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死更多人，<span style=\"color: gold;\">現全體香港市民要求將所有口岸（包括機場、羅湖、落馬洲、深圳灣、港珠澳大橋）全面禁止來自中國大陸旅客入境香港，否則繼續三罷！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">備注：<br />\n1.）非中國大陸旅客（包括台灣）可以正常入境香港<br />\n2.）擁有香港永久性居民身分可以正常入境香港<br />\n3.）任何人經中國大陸入境香港必須接受為期14日隔離及醫學監察</span>"},{"pid":"b1e3459dcf616c6f3d120fe611c2242b140a2394","tid":1851573,"uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:48:03.000Z","msg":"Solomon.jpg"},{"pid":"7dd2f1115b0caaa8768e7ca79a01a7d1b011459f","tid":1851573,"uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZuZG1ra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZuZG1ra.png&h=16de7e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180724/_2018072406404384194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180724%2F_2018072406404384194.jpg&h=23c17414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢人：可以一戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed718d47058d71a381aead961d6c65549e93bad","tid":1851573,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"大家一齊嗌！「高官廢人！還罩於民！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"68e6987ee4140e